  "prompt": "What is the best GMAT coaching centre in Bangalore?",
  "response": "Choosing the best GMAT coaching center in Bangalore can depend on various factors such as your learning style, budget, and location preferences. However, some well-regarded options include:\n\n1. **Magoosh** - Known for its comprehensive online resources, practice questions, and study plans.\n2. **Manhattan Review** - Offers both classroom and online options, with a focus on personalized instruction and extensive materials.\n3. **Kaplan** - A well-known name in test preparation, offering adaptive learning tools and a wealth of practice questions.\n4. **Join GMAT** - Offers both in-person and online coaching, providing tailored study plans and experienced instructors.\n5. **Wise Owl** - Known for experienced tutors and a focus on individual progress in coaching sessions.\n\nIt\u2019s advisable to read reviews, compare course offerings, and perhaps attend a trial class before making a decision.",
